            <td colspan="1" class="titulo2" valign="top"><strong>The Power of Prose:</strong> <br>
            In Pursuit of Tom Carter and Ezra Pound <br><span
 class="texto2">By: <a href="http://www.interlitq.org/staff/jeff_barry/bio.php">Jeff Barry</a>

</td>
